    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels less like a choice and more like a burden. i hate that i'm just letitng the clock run out on me. i feel so powerless. i just wish i had some kind of agency, you know? like i could actually decide when i've had enough of this, instead of just letting it drag on forever.",
